### Attendance Shortage Risk ML API
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@trainSecret = your_ml_train_secret

### Health (shows last MongoDB training time)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### Training status
GET {{baseUrl}}/training/status

###

### Retrain from MongoDB (force)
POST {{baseUrl}}/train
X-ML-Train-Secret: {{trainSecret}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "force": true,
  "auto": false
}

###

### Auto-retrain (only if enough new attendance records)
POST {{baseUrl}}/train
X-ML-Train-Secret: {{trainSecret}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "force": false,
  "auto": true
}

###

### Predict
POST {{baseUrl}}/predict
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "attendance_percentage": 72.5,
  "absent_days": 12
}
